channel.title: Can My Router Not Port Forward?
channel.description:
I have done everything needed to be able to port forward. I even had someone go through and check over TV and he said that he doesn't know why it's not working. Can someone who's experienced with Netgear routers check on TV for me? Specifically router WPN824v2.
And yes, I have been to portforward.com.

item.title: Can My Router Not Port Forward?
item.dc:creator: @niggerlove25 niggerlove25
item.description:
@niggerlove25 wrote:

Well from past experience, i have also ran into the same problem. I had my buddy witch is a java programmer take a look at my computer. And he explained that everything was done correctly. He said the only thing it could possibly be is my router. So i went and bought a new one the next week. Set it up, and i portfoward. and it worked! Im not saying go spend money on a new router, and it not work. But that was my problem.
